Package: simOutcome
Type: Package
Title: Simulation of Outcomes for Classification and Regression Models
Version: 0.1.0
Maintainer: Piotr Tymoszuk <piotr.s.tymoszuk@gmail.com>
Description: A still growing development package that simulated continuous, 
    as well as binary and multi-categorical modeling outcomes with 
    user-specified characteristics such as error, specificity, sensitivity, 
    kappa or Brier score.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
